  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the World of Dragons. Dragon Simulator Multiplayer is a 3D simulator game in which you fight in PVP battles against other dragons or finish off AI characters that shoot from the ground. You can also play a cooperative game mode in which you have to kill zombies and collect their souls.<br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Controllable mighty dragon<br></li><li>3 maps to play<br></li><li>Multiple dragon skins<br></li><li>Multiple dragon attacks: fireball, fire breath, and special<br></li><li>4 game modes: death-match, team death-match, Battle Royale, Zombie mode (cooperative)<br></li><li>Day and night time options</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to the World of Dragons. Dragon Simulator Multiplayer is a 3D simulator game in which you fight in PVP battles against other dragons or finish off AI characters that shoot from the ground. You can also play a cooperative game mode in which you have to kill zombies and collect their souls.<br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Controllable mighty dragon<br></li><li>3 maps to play<br></li><li>Multiple dragon skins<br></li><li>Multiple dragon attacks: fireball, fire breath, and special<br></li><li>4 game modes: death-match, team death-match, Battle Royale, Zombie mode (cooperative)<br></li><li>Day and night time options</li></ul>",
